Makenzie Vega https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Makenzie_Vega 0 Makenzie Vega (born February 10, 1994) is an American actress. She is known for her role as Grace Florrick on The Good Wife and as the 11-year-old counterpart of Nancy Callahan in Sin City. Makenzie_Vega ( born February_10_,_1994 ) is an_American_actress .
